data.description: PRIVATE WELL! *Priced below appraisal*  Horse property on 2.3 acres near McDowell Mtn Park with mountain views! Circle drive, charming courtyard. Interior has flagstone floors, soaring ceilings, light alder cabinets, canyon colored granite. Back of house has wall of windows and sliders to showcase patios and views. Two guest bedrooms with ensuite bath and private patio. Office with closet. Large primary bedroom and bath, walk-in closets that go forever. North side of house 2000 sq ft addition could be studio, guest quarters, multi-gen living, separate entrance with private patio. Spacious, many windows and closets.  Horse barn, arena, 4 stalls with runs or 8 stalls. Tack room, hay storage. Ride, hike or bike from property to beautiful McDowell Mtn Park, 22,000 acres. Solar panels, owned.
